{"tid":2126074,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"刷牙流曬血","createTime":"2020-07-26T15:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T15:47:40.000Z","uid":207822,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dc589431800853f338bd65223adec79420e9b28f","tid":2126074,"uid":207822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T15:37:02.000Z","msg":"最近刷牙有幾個位啲牙肉不斷流血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲泡變到粉紅色 漱口漱左一陣先止血<br />\n<br />\n有時就算唔係刷牙 純粹舐下啲牙肉都會流血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前仲覺得係熱氣先咁<br />\n而家真係覺得要睇牙醫<br />\n想問下如果咁流牙血我係去洗牙定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對上個次睇牙醫已經係小學既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06852be6d3782ff2a9b6b2b02de0b5bb739253a","tid":2126074,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T15:38:14.000Z","msg":"牙周病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c6f694e9c8471f3651892d882baf5cbc9884429","tid":2126074,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T15:39:37.000Z","msg":"流牙血唔關有冇洗牙事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你十年唔洗牙都唔會洗牙血"},{"pid":"14db28b541f3354b90d62da0a7a88c0dea5ba6f1","tid":2126074,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T15:40:41.000Z","msg":"牙肉問題"},{"pid":"704aba5d02f0c46941636cf59f122bd464968fbc","tid":2126074,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c6f694e9c8471f3651892d882baf5cbc9884429","tid":2126074,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T15:39:37.000Z","msg":"流牙血唔關有冇洗牙事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你十年唔洗牙都唔會洗牙血"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime